468
00:32:28,662 --> 00:32:30,095
Michael Raymond Clayton.

469
00:32:30,264 --> 00:32:35,167
<i>Born September 9, 1959,
St. Joseph's Hospital, Bronx, New York.</i>

470
00:32:35,335 --> 00:32:39,032
