477
00:32:59,993 --> 00:33:01,927
<i>... Organized Crime Task Force.</i>

478
00:33:02,095 --> 00:33:05,496
And then in 1990, he starts
at Kenner, Bach & Ledeen.

479
00:33:05,666 --> 00:33:07,099
