680
00:45:56,669 --> 00:45:57,897
I was punting.

681
00:45:58,071 --> 00:46:00,733
You gotta saddle up here
and get things under control.

682
00:46:00,907 --> 00:46:01,896
Saddle up?

683
00:46:02,075 --> 00:46:05,135
